# trackIDs

**Instance Property**

The IDs of the tracks in the group.

## Declaration

```swift
var trackIDs: [NSNumber] { get }
```

## Discussion

The value of this property is an array of [doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/Foundation/NSNumber] instances used as [doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/CoreMedia/CMPersistentTrackID] values, one for each track in the group.
